<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>١١- كَذَّبَتْ قَوْمُ نُوحٍ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٠٥)</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>إِذْ قالَ لَهُمْ أَخُوهُمْ نُوحٌ أَلا تَتَّقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٠٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٥»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>١٢- كَذَّبَتْ عادٌ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٢٣)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>إِذْ قالَ لَهُمْ أَخُوهُمْ هُودٌ أَلا تَتَّقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٢٤)</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِنِّي لَكُمْ رَسُولٌ أَمِينٌ <span class="c2">(١٢٥)</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>فَاتَّقُوا اللَّهَ وَأَطِيعُونِ <span class="c2">(١٢٦)</span> <span class="c2">«٦»</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>١٣- كَذَّبَتْ ثَمُودُ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٤١)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>إِذْ قالَ لَهُمْ أَخُوهُمْ صالِحٌ أَلا تَتَّقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٤٢)</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>إِنِّي لَكُمْ رَسُولٌ أَمِينٌ <span class="c2">(١٤٣)</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَاتَّقُوا اللَّهَ وَأَطِيعُونِ <span class="c2">(١٤٤)</span> <span class="c2">«٧»</span><a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>١٤- كَذَّبَتْ قَوْمُ لُوطٍ الْمُرْسَلِينَ <span class="c2">(١٦٠)</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إِذْ قالَ لَهُمْ أَخُوهُمْ لُوطٌ أَلا تَتَّقُونَ <span class="c2">(١٦١)</span> <span class="c2">«٨»</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>١٥- وَلَقَدْ أَرْسَلْنا إِلى ثَمُودَ أَخاهُمْ صالِحاً أَنِ اعْبُدُوا اللَّهَ فَإِذا هُمْ فَرِيقانِ يَخْتَصِمُونَ <span class="c2">(٤٥)</span> <span class="c2">«٩»</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
